org.aludratest.service.gui.web.page
Class Page

java.lang.Object
  org.aludratest.service.gui.web.page.Page
All Implemented Interfaces:
ActionWordLibrary<Page>
public abstract class Page
extends Object
implements ActionWordLibrary<Page>

A Page is the base class for every new class which shall provide access to a web page of the application under test. With extension of this class every sub class is of the type AludraTest, it can perform low level actions on the application under test and it gets the power to use common UIMaps.

Author:
Marcel Malitz, Volker Bergmann

protected abstract void checkCorrectPage()
